nd I couldn’t help myself. I think there’s a bulb out.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":{"line":"Yeah, parasailing. Always wanted to try that.","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"May","first":{"line":"No.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":{"line":"Parasailing?","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Daisy","first":{"line":"The secret is out. For decades, your organization stayed in the shadows. Hiding the truth. But now we know — they’re among us. Heroes… and monsters. The world is full of wonders.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":{"line":"All right, Director, where to first?","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Fitz","first":{"line":"Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa! Watch it! That’s the night-night gun.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":{"line":"Okay… Hey, Mack. I think my leg’s broken.","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Simmons","first":{"line":"Well, it’s on my stuff, and it doesn’t work, and there’s no way we’re calling it the night-night gun.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":{"line":"None of us do.","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Ward","first":{"line":"I’m five minutes away from retrieving it.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":{"line":"You, too.","episode_id":"s04e19","episode_title":"All the Madame's Men"}},{"character":"Mack","first":{"line":"♪ High and low I’ve traveled ♪ ♪ Far and wide I’d go ♪ ♪ From the desert tracks to the mountainside ♪ ♪ I’ll bring you this traveling show ♪","episode_id":"s01e03","episode_title":"The Asset"},"last":{"line":"Probably gonna call you every chance I can, for advice.","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Hunter","first":{"line":"The mystery I’d like to solve is, why should we be paying you so much? This looks like a box. Sorry… a picture of a box… a picture of a box you don’t have.","episode_id":"s02e01","episode_title":"Shadows"},"last":{"line":"I love you.","episode_id":"s05e05","episode_title":"Rewind"}},{"character":"Bobbi","first":{"line":"Keep everyone off their phones and tablets. We have a mole, ladies and gentlemen, right here in our very facility. Someone has been sending S.H.I.E.L.D. messages right under our noses. I specialize in finding them. Bakshi here… well, he makes them suffer. Until that happens… no one leaves.","episode_id":"s02e05","episode_title":"A Hen in the Wolf House"},"last":{"line":"It’s a spy’s goodbye.","episode_id":"s03e13","episode_title":"Parting Shot"}},{"character":"Yo-Yo","first":{"line":"So, you’re not going to change my grade?","episode_id":"s01e08","episode_title":"The Well"},"last":{"line":"Thank you, boss.","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Deke","first":{"line":"I’ve been looking for you.","episode_id":"s05e01","episode_title":"Orientation (Part One)"},"last":{"line":"They spotted him?","episode_id":"s05e22","episode_title":"The End"}},{"character":"Triplett","first":{"line":"An honor, sir.","episode_id":"s01e14","episode_title":"T.A.H.I.T.I."},"last":{"line":"She doesn’t know what happened. I was waiting till tomorrow to tell her, but I guess I don’t have to now. Hey. Hey, look who’s here.","episode_id":"s04e20","episode_title":"Farewell, Cruel World!"}},{"character":"Hill","first":{"line":"What does “S.H.I.E.L.D.” stand for, Agent Ward?","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":null},{"character":"Fury","first":{"line":"Really? Really, Coulson? Six days? It only took you six days to take a completely renovated piece of state-of-the-art machinery and turn it into scrap?!","episode_id":"s01e02","episode_title":"0-8-4"},"last":null},{"character":"Garrett","first":{"line":"Well, as opposed to the level 8 jackass I’m staring at, I still follow orders.","episode_id":"s01e14","episode_title":"T.A.H.I.T.I."},"last":null},{"character":"Raina","first":{"line":"How did you do that?","episode_id":"s01e05","episode_title":"Girl in the Flower Dress"},"last":null},{"character":"Talbot","first":{"line":"This is Colonel Glenn Talbot, U.S. Air force. I need to speak with whoever’s in charge over there.","episode_id":"s01e18","episode_title":"Providence"},"last":null},{"character":"Lincoln","first":{"line":"You’re healing. Leaving now wouldn’t exactly be… You ever made microwave popcorn? Leave it in too long, and it’s charcoal. Take it out too soon, and it’s a bag of kernels. That might be the worst analogy ever. Gordo, help me out here.","episode_id":"s02e16","episode_title":"Afterlife"},"last":null},{"character":"Hive","first":{"line":"I’m hungry.","episode_id":"s03e11","episode_title":"Bouncing Back"},"last":null},{"character":"Robbie","first":{"line":"Left it for who?","episode_id":"s04e01","episode_title":"The Ghost"},"last":null},{"character":"Aida","first":{"line":"Welcome back, Dr. Radcliffe.","episode_id":"s03e22","episode_title":"Ascension"},"last":null},{"character":"Peterson","first":{"line":"Thanks, Bernie.","episode_id":"s01e01","episode_title":"Pilot"},"last":null},{"character":"Calvin","first":{"line":"You did well.","episode_id":"s02e02","episode_title":"Heavy Is the Head"},"last":null},{"character":"Jiaying","first":{"line":"Poor thing. How long since he passed through the mist?","episode_id":"s02e11","episode_title":"Aftershocks"},"last":null}]}